des: Broadcasting live from Los Angeles, Safiri Radio is your internet radio source for an eclectic mix of urban music from around the world. From R&B and hip-hop to Afrobeats, jazz, gospel, house, old skool and more, Safiri Radio keeps you connected to the hottest beats and emerging artists. Available 24/7, Safiri Radio is your ultimate music companion at home, work or on the go. More Music. More Variety. We are Safiri Radio, Your Eclectic Urban Music Mix.
